tlantic, easyJet or Monarch would follow suit with their own Brexit-related promotions.\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 1145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brexit vote is causing real anxiety among many U.K. companies: The parent company of British Airways, as well as discount airline easyJet, both warned that their profits could take a hit this year.\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Virgin Atlantic founder Sir Richard Branson, meanwhile, said he suspects that his Virgin Group holding company has lost a third in value since the vote.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1501, \"entities\": []}]}"